{"tid":42982,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Ubisoft 30特別周末活動！7款月贈遊戲限期免費下載 大家唔好執輸","createTime":"2016-12-17T06:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T14:43:26.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41dc614593f3cf5957d7c42ad0c20512f100e53b","tid":42982,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/files/a21f9fa71fa2e7567d1b60d8d24257ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Ffiles%2Fa21f9fa71fa2e7567d1b60d8d24257ab.jpg&h=15af0891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好消息！Ubisoft 為了歡慶 30 週年，早在今年夏天便開始舉辦的每月免費遊戲贈送，如今這些遊戲已全面限期免費下載，即日起至 <span style=\"color: red;\">12 月 18 日</span>（日）止，玩家們皆可進入官方活動頁面，登入個人 uplay 帳號來一口氣獲得 7 款遊戲的組合包！<br />\n <br />\n原本這些遊戲作為官方為了慶祝 30 週年的月贈免費商品，當月期限一過便無法再次獲得，不過就在聖誕節的前夕，佛心公司 Ubisoft 再給了所有錯過玩家一次機會，讓玩家得以擁有之前沒能來得及下載的免費遊戲。從 6 月開始的《波斯王子：時之砂》、7 月的《縱橫諜海》、8 月的《雷射超人：起源》、9 月的《飆酷車神（Crew）》、10 月《神鬼冒險》、11 月的《極地戰嚎 3：血龍》，以及目前 12 月最夯的《刺客教條 3》，讓玩家在用戶端下載時甚至擠爆了 uplay 伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n想要獲得遊戲的玩家，只要進入官方活動頁面登入個人 uplay 帳號，即可獲得遊戲，屆時再開啟 uplay 用戶端程式進行下載遊戲即可。<br />\n<a href=\"https://club.ubisoft.com/en-GB/ubi30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclub.ubisoft.com%2Fen-GB%2Fubi30&d=KBe1arX0TEC7Xq1RNJa2OnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7981f2dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://club.ubisoft.com/en-GB/ubi30</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/31054/ubi-30-anniversary-monthly-free-game-all-downloadable-for-now\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F31054%2Fubi-30-anniversary-monthly-free-game-all-downloadable-for-now&d=KBe1arX0TEC7Xq1RNJa2OnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6f2cdd01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/31054/ubi-30-anniversary-monthly-free-game-all-downloadable-for-now</a>"},{"pid":"82f00bea8f57b5142c45e25875bcc960157c70e1","tid":42982,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:34:33.000Z","msg":"今日最後機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfd3a21c818e72c7c16eed6927d95abc106537e","tid":42982,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左街 睇嚟dl 唔切"},{"pid":"03b7bf1a5713fbb05840bcbd462de25976d97006","tid":42982,"uid":51670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"應該可以拎咗先唔dl住"},{"pid":"1807ba30ec9e0bb622292ff848bae6c78a78b482","tid":42982,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左街 睇嚟dl 唔切</blockquote><br />\n可以唔DL住<br />\n但要註冊個Ubisoft AC留起左先<br />\n遲D可以用佢個UPLAY DL返"},{"pid":"6b26f87706b8b6639a81c82d6720be9be777eab6","tid":42982,"uid":64816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日最後機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7773eade7a012de155a8c947ca9c0e40f244583","tid":42982,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/vWaZz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FvWaZz.jpg&h=8aa8d791&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}